[None of the reports above are complete but it seems that the parcel was delivered to the PM's residence on 18 Oct 2011, referred to the CSIR laboratory at some point, and _Bacillus anthracis_ spores identified some time in January 2012. The source, a lady professor at Jamshoro University, has presumably been interviewed but as yet no arrests have been announced. It will be interesting to see how it all works out from such a confusing start. - Mod.MHJ

